newsitem.title: NETHERLANDS: SOCCER-DUTCH FIRST DIVISION MATCH SUMMARY.
newsitem.headline: SOCCER-DUTCH FIRST DIVISION MATCH SUMMARY.

text.p: Summary of Tuesday's Dutch first division match:
Sparta Rotterdam 1 (Renfurm 87) AZ Alkmaar 2 (Fortes Rodrigues 25, Bociek 35). Halftime 0-2. Attendance 3,000.
